Nothing OS — Screen Recorder
Unified with control/volume/network/bluetooth design language:
  - red glyph dot in header
  - hero dot-matrix REC indicator with pulse
  - CircleButton toggles for options
  - flat last-file row
  - bug fix: fullscreen recording (auto-detect output)
"""

import os
